      Yoga Therapy treats people with health issues. Research provides evidence that it can help alleviate many ailments, including back pain, hypertension, heart conditions, asthma, diabetes and stress. This type of yoga uses gentle exercises,
      meditation, relaxation and breathing techniques to help restore physical and emotional equilibrium. </p>

