      <p class="hp "><em> 2.Phoenix Rising Yoga Therapy</em></p>
      <p class="pb">Pheonix Yoga Therapy does not deal with curing a particular type of ailment. Instead, it takes into account what the clients need, i.e., whether he wants to work on mental stability or physical fitness. In Pheonix Yoga Therapy
        instructor focus on assisted yoga poses, body psychology, breathing techniques and proper body mechanics. It helps you in stress management, healing trauma, overcoming relationship issues, dealing with menopause, cancer healing and aging.</p>
    </div>

